in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"我是一名水名的学生@曾经有幸与一名少有的@从大东转来的学生一同学习"},{"narration":"但是，当时的我@不仅全盘听信了东边的传闻@还很嫉妒优秀的她@最后对她做了很过分的事情…"},{"narration":"不，根本不只是过分@我当时是想把她从楼梯上推下去"},{"narration":"虽然不觉得那时候犯下的罪行@能靠一次署名就偿还干净@但我想以此为契机改变自己"},{"narration":"我想在改变自己的同时@让不幸的人不再增加"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_14033.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103801,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":103801,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-27"}],"nameRight":"御影","textRight":"大家或许只是@没能直率地说出真心话而已","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101001,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-28"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"只是因为相同的人聚集了起来@看起来很多而已"},{"chara":[{"id":101001,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-29"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"实际上，这里的只是@神滨市的学生的一部分"},{"chara":[{"id":101001,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-30"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"考虑到人口总数，@真的是微乎其微的数字…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103801,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-31"}],"nameRight":"御影","textRight":"但是，桃碳"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101001,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-32"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"对，这并不是个小数目@是可以由我们来改变的"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":103801,"motion":200,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-10-33"}],"nameRight":"御影","textRight":"嗯"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_01","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":103801},{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_01","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101001}],"se":"7201_detect_magic","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":